          "type": "rtf",
          "settings": {
            "richtext_content": "<p>Luke Powell is the visionary founder of Shred Fast, a revolutionary fitness program focused on transforming both the body and mind. With over 15 years of dedicated experience in the health and fitness industry, his mission is clear: to inspire, motivate, and empower individuals on their wellness journey. Now, as a Gym King ambassador, Luke continues to inspire others to push their limits.</p><h3>Career Highlights</h3><p><strong>Founder of Shred Fast</strong>: Creator of the Shred Fast program, known for its high-intensity, results-driven approach to fitness and fat loss.</p><p><strong>Professional Athlete: </strong>Professional football, MMA cage, boxing and national-level athletics.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
