    "content_rich_text_GChbfX": {
      "type": "content-rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "quote_tEnDNg": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote_text": "I’ve walked diverse paths – from professional football to the MMA cage, boxing ring, and national-level athletics. Countless workshops and personal trials have equipped me with the tools for a resilient body and mind, all masterfully integrated into the ShredFast program. Since then ShredFast has grown exponentially. From just myself and website developer, to now a team of 15. The unique thing is, each member of the team has used the programme to better their lives before joining the team. <br><br> When lockdowns disrupted our lives, I seized the opportunity to launch our website and introduce a subscription-based program. Since then, ShredFast’s remarkable growth is evident, evolving from a humble duo consisting of myself and a web designer to a robust team of 15 dedicated individuals.",
            "quote_author": ""
          }
        },
        "rtf_UyxD3X": {
          "type": "rtf",
          "settings": {
            "richtext_content": "<p>ShredFast has become a game-changer for countless individuals looking to level up their fitness. Watch Luke and his team take you through some of the signature moves you’ll see throughout the program.</p><h3>Why is ShredFast different?</h3><p>“What sets ShredFast apart is the extraordinary fact that every team member has personally experienced the transformative power of the ShredFast program before becoming an integral part of our team. This unique approach not only fosters a deep understanding of our mission but also showcases the program’s efficacy in elevating individuals, making our team a true testament to the program’s success”.</p>"
          }
